<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en"><p><a href="https://twitter.com/NLE_Ninja" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://twitter.com']);">@NLE_Ninja</a> they&#8217;re my favorite. 3 on my desk right now <a href="http://t.co/lPKrdCekCw" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://t.co']);">pic.twitter.com/lPKrdCekCw</a></p>
<p>— Josh Short (@shortedits) <a href="https://twitter.com/shortedits/statuses/411570765201682432" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://twitter.com']);">December 13, 2013</a></p></blockquote>
<p><script async src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p>
<p>Editor Josh Short tweeted about these Fantom Drives (which I&#8217;ve never heard of or used, as they&#8217;re not available in the UK) but if you&#8217;re interested you can <a title="Fantom Drives on Amazon" href="http://www.amazon.com/s/?_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;pageMinusResults=1&amp;suo=1392478067749&amp;tag=jonelwfiledi-20&amp;url=search-alias%3Daps#/ref=nb_sb_noss_1?url=search-alias%3Daps&amp;field-keywords=fantom%20drives&amp;sprefix=fanto%2Caps&amp;rh=i%3Aaps%2Ck%3Afantom%20drives&amp;sepatfbtf=true&amp;tc=1392478074109" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://www.amazon.com']);" target="_blank">check them out here on Amazon.com</a>. <a title="The Quad Pro Fantom Drive" href="http://www.fantomdrives.com/products/quad-pro.html#.Uv-IZ0J_sbw" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://www.fantomdrives.com']);" target="_blank">The Quad Pro</a> or <a title="Geforce 3 Mini" href="http://www.fantomdrives.com/products/gforce3-mini.html#.Uv-JAEJ_sbw" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://www.fantomdrives.com']);" target="_blank">Geforce 3 Mini&#8217;s</a> look particularly good.</p>
